{"tid":2498839,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"保安局再三澄清：新通報機制下 港人仍有離境自由","createTime":"2021-04-21T12:23:18.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-21T12:36:18.000Z","uid":21470,"like":1,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"96f712924af37461b79669db8f7c063bea5d5272","tid":2498839,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T12:23:18.000Z","msg":"保安局強烈譴責於網媒刊登有關《2020年入境（修訂）條例草案》文章內容失實及誤導<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n  就有組織今日（四月二十一日）在網媒刊登的一篇文章內容對《2020年入境（修訂）條例草案》下有關賦權保安局局長就運輸工具提供乘客資料訂立規例的條文作出失實和誤導性的敍述，並在社交媒體發放，保安局對此予以強烈譴責。<br />\n <br />\n  保安局發言人指出，條例草案下建議加入有關賦權條文，目的是為了履行香港特別行政區在《國際民用航空公約》下的國際責任，以推行預報旅客資料系統。政府在提交立法會條例草案委員會的文件和在草案委員會的會議上，已多次向立法會議員和公眾清楚解釋，有關系統的目的是要求來港而非離港的航機提供乘客資料，並不會對香港居民出入境自由有任何影響。對於個別組織刻意發放失實信息及故意曲解有關條文的立法目的和背景，藉此散播謠言，誤導市民，企圖抹黑立法程序，保安局對此表示極度不滿，須直斥其非。<br />\n <br />\n  發言人強調：「對於居心叵測的人故意誤導市民，蠱惑人心，保安局必須強烈譴責，以正視聽。」<br />\n<br />\n  他表示：「根據《國際民用航空公約》的要求，所有成員須推行預報旅客資料系統，並賦以法律效力。按照有關規定，航空公司須在航機起飛赴港前，向入境事務處提供所有乘客及機組人員的資料。這只會適用於入境的航班。現時，已有超過90個國家推行該系統，包括歐盟成員國、美國、加拿大及澳洲等。」<br />\n <br />\n  國際民用航空組織引入預報旅客資料系統是為了提升國際民航保安，同時便利世界各地出入境管制機關對旅客實施更有效管制，而政府防範潛在免遣返聲請人抵港的措施亦可隨之加強。事實上，立法會已就防止免遣返聲請的機制被濫用長期跟進有關事項，包括在保安事務委員會多次討論及成立特別小組委員會審議不同相關議題。<br />\n <br />\n  發言人亦指出：「按照一般做法，在主體法例中訂明的賦權條文一般會較為概括，然後根據賦權條文而擬備的附屬法例會訂明具體細節和清晰條文。制定有關規例的過程亦須再經立法會審議及通過。政府稍後制定的規例將會充分反映出來，並會訂明相關的具體細節。此外，在落實有關系統前，我們會諮詢航空業界及不同持份者的意見，亦需要向立法會財務委員會申請撥款。」<br />\n <br />\n  發言人強調：「香港居民的旅行和出入境自由受《基本法》第三十一條所保障。在政府向立法會提交條例草案前，我們已確定所有條文均符合《基本法》，包括有關人權的條文。因此，我們認為沒有需要在主體法例提及有關權力不會對香港居民、以及有權進入並留港人士的權利造成任何影響。」<br />\n <br />\n  立法會條例草案委員會早前已經詳細審視條例草案每項條文，並向政府作出提問。其間，政府已就有關系統及擬議條文的背景和目的詳細解答議員及個別團體的提問。條例草案將於四月二十八日立法會會議上恢復二讀。如獲立法會通過，修訂條例將於八月一日生效；政府亦會着手擬備有關預報旅客資料系統的附屬法例，並會適時諮詢持份者及立法會的意見。<br />\n <br />\n完<br />\n2021年4月21日（星期三）<br />\n香港時間19時40分<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202104/21/P2021042100723.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F202104%2F21%2FP2021042100723.htm&d=Hmcjt6vcQR8GyvD5m8y4dOm6EOSy25kVi46SvbSXLY8%3D&h=adbbebfb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202104/21/P2021042100723.htm</a>"},{"pid":"96554ad8096c54ec09d0c56be9cf0f7c3b3c1420","tid":2498839,"uid":374427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T12:24:02.000Z","msg":"連登仔李伯盧開Patreon，需要大家支持！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2498797\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2498797</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"83859b33c404a86380d27b3ae3ec53e5cb2c9f6e","tid":2498839,"uid":53062,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T12:24:12.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">依法</span></span>享有出境自由"},{"pid":"b282e982f2ab1a29ac5308854912e1a46ec54e56","tid":2498839,"uid":127575,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T12:24:12.000Z","msg":"即係沒有離境自由<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n八月份玩機場大封鎖<br />\n出得聲明...多數相反就啱"},{"pid":"1de1e073561d4da7ab348805000071aa88bfc0dc","tid":2498839,"uid":20170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T12:27:36.000Z","msg":"邊個網媒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e5e27a529583c19bb0cf10db30eabf68447e399","tid":2498839,"uid":34213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T12:28:16.000Z","msg":"封關lu"},{"pid":"f0cb2c884748c27b2e52c964e512d2b58cc972f5","tid":2498839,"uid":82938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T12:28:33.000Z","msg":"遊行集會自由"},{"pid":"50cffec8c9381de5150f95a132c839be31b0902e","tid":2498839,"uid":12991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T12:28:36.000Z","msg":"即係有 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"889acecb832ef854124b9bb2eac1e61f7ec99025","tid":2498839,"uid":385411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T12:29:19.000Z","msg":"講得出即係就玩完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7816f6eb38ec0942b85916d0f549bc9428759dee","tid":2498839,"uid":82639,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T12:29:59.000Z","msg":"政府澄清完，就明白了，安心曬🙂"},{"pid":"74cca23afbb11915bc14e730774454fb5e5f4ee6","tid":2498839,"uid":171506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T12:30:54.000Z","msg":"基本法賦與?"},{"pid":"0ca9defee41420b182f4752ff95b5c2e1f571efc","tid":2498839,"uid":147348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T12:31:05.000Z","msg":"咁即係無自由啦，明曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5b092a65e179ff47668f6b36f83ccbdfa5a1702","tid":2498839,"uid":166080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T12:31:20.000Z","msg":"更加確定支共會鎖港"},{"pid":"60b98183ef280a91e270808c8b61170051c48a48","tid":2498839,"uid":15880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T12:31:29.000Z","msg":"死左咪有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"541bc856c8902c564d8990e99285bc81badec22b","tid":2498839,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T12:32:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210217/QF2ORO6YTZDYDBL2DOW2AYM27Y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210217%2FQF2ORO6YTZDYDBL2DOW2AYM27Y%2F&d=Hmcjt6vcQR8GyvD5m8y4dOm6EOSy25kVi46SvbSXLY8%3D&h=57ed0772\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210217%2FQF2ORO6YTZDYDBL2DOW2AYM27Y%2F&h=9108661a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210217/QF2ORO6YTZDYDBL2DOW2AYM27Y/</a><br />\n\t<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】港府早前向立法會提交《2020年入境（修訂）條例草案》，擬加快免遣返聲請審核程序，大律師公會就草案第3條發出意見書，指該例賦權保安局禁止港人出境，擔心權力遭受濫用。保安局日前出稿辯稱草案不會對香港居民出入境自由有任何影響，批評公會引起不必要誤解。大律師公會因應當局的說法，昨晚再發出聲明，建議進一步收窄草案中保安局的權力，清楚列明只在針對入境航班、而非離境航班的情況時，才有權禁止該人登上運輸工具。<br />\n<br />\n當局於《2020年入境（修訂）條例草案》擬加入新訂的第6A條，賦權保安局局長訂立規例，以向入境處處長提供飛機上乘客及機組人員資料，並容許其指示飛機禁止運載某乘客或乘組人員，保安局辯稱有關權力只涉及入境乘客及機組人員，以防範免遣返聲請人抵港，故不會影響港人出入境自由。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n反映立法原意<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。大律師公會又認為，草案的主體法例亦應進一步說明，有關權力不會對香港居民，以及有權進入並留港人士的權利造成任何影響。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"orange\">大律師公會上周就草案提交意見書，指出修訂將授權局方禁止任何人離開香港，但卻未有解釋允許其行使權力的理由，形容如同授權其「明顯不受限制的權力」，情況令人感到不安</span>。。。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"acc1fed04cf0f9eb65c4eefa111015f2abd20d77","tid":2498839,"uid":18477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"60b98183ef280a91e270808c8b61170051c48a48","tid":2498839,"uid":15880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T12:31:29.000Z","msg":"死左咪有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T12:33:19.000Z","msg":"而家所謂嘅綠色殯葬有得撒落海咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b9cb380375446649ea222b2582dd1a0c024e55f","tid":2498839,"uid":73565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T12:33:38.000Z","msg":"市民的確有離境自由<br />\n不過政府因疫情禁止所有航班升降<br />\n大家可以選擇去中國<br />\n有得揀去定唔去 十分自由"},{"pid":"df0916f253be42f0266d3714b31cccb073e57d28","tid":2498839,"uid":2615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T12:34:02.000Z","msg":"得喇<br />\n收皮啦"},{"pid":"665499285fba40876b30046143b352804f15fb59","tid":2498839,"uid":33028,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T12:34:14.000Z","msg":"有得走快啲快，到時冇得走唔好賴人。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96bd773c8fd2899879bfa66ae5e7d3b1ab15e755","tid":2498839,"uid":189650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T12:35:36.000Z","msg":"哦，清楚明白"},{"pid":"6393a2238c4e890729d8d8bde9013e4860be6937","tid":2498839,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T12:36:18.000Z","msg":"離境要通報架?<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/annoyed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/annoyed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}